[B]2.[/B] Then take the contents of "[B]yourgamemod[/B]" from "[B]configuration_files.zip[/B]", to your gamemod folder.

[B]3.[/B] [B]Compile[/B] the files and put the [B]compiled[/B] files to your plugins folder at
