[B]4.[/B] Put the next lines to your "[B]plugins.ini[/B]" file at "[COLOR="Blue"]yourgamemod/addons/amxmodx/[/COLOR][B]configs[/B]" and
[B][COLOR="Red"]disable[/COLOR][/B] the original "[B]mapchooser.amxx[/B]":
