; Choose
galileo.amxx
[/QUOTE]

[B]5.[/B] Put the next line to your "[B]amxx.cfg[/B]" file at "[COLOR="Blue"]yourgamemod/addons/amxmodx/[/COLOR][B]configs[/B]":
